comments: Forbes (SAS) makes marginal contact with Fultz (ORL) during the drive, but does not affect his SQBR.
Fournier (ORL) collapses his forearm against his body and makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) body as he swipes down, but does not make contact to DeRozan's arm.
Ross (ORL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Aldridge (SAS) as they briefly interlock arms, but immediately disengage.
DeRozan (SAS) makes clean hand to ball contact.
Vucevic (ORL) briefly grasps Aldridge's (SAS) arm, but does not affect his ability to defend off ball.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of DeRozan (SAS) and absorbs the contact.
Fournier (ORL) is moving alongside DeRozan's (SAS) path and he maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Fultz (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during White's (SAS) driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) makes marginal contact to Vucevic's (ORL) arm as he is releasing the pass, but the contact does not affect his ability to pass.
DeRozan (SAS) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps after the gather.
Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact to Lyles' (SAS) body after his release and does not affect his play at the basket.
DeRozan (SAS) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
As Fournier's (ORL) momentum is carrying him out of bounds, Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with him, but does not affect his ability to stay in-bounds and complete the pass.
All Flagrant Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Mills (SAS) and Vucevic (ORL) engage and disengage during the inbound play.
Mills (SAS) makes contact to Vucevic's (ORL) body which affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Fournier (ORL) makes contact to DeRozan's (SAS) arm on the rip-through.
DeRozan (SAS) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
